I"Î<h2 id="handwriting">Handwriting</h2>

<p><strong>Goal:</strong> Write numbers legibly.</p>

<p><strong>Materials:</strong> Attached Document (coming soon!)</p>

<h3 id="1st-challenge-fill-a-spot-with-a-number">1st Challenge: Fill a Spot with a Number</h3>
<p>Fill each spot with a number.
Completed if: Each number is legible.
Otherwise, follow up with: Pick 1 number to practice writing. (Be creative. Chalk, markers, paint, anything counts.)</p>

<h3 id="2nd-challenge-fill-a-spot-with-a-different-number">2nd Challenge: Fill a Spot with a Different Number</h3>
<p>Fill each spot with a <em>different</em> number.
Same completion/follow up.</p>

<p>When both challenges are finished, move to next Writing Task.</p>
